  • Package Summary 
    Package Description
    org.mybatis.guice
    Contains core classes to build the MyBatis stuff through Google Guice.
    org.mybatis.guice.binder
    The MyBatis module EDSL.
    org.mybatis.guice.configuration
    Contains core classes to build the iBatis Configuration through google-guice.
    org.mybatis.guice.configuration.settings  
    org.mybatis.guice.datasource.builtin
    Contains core classes to build the myBatis DataSource implementations through google-guice.
    org.mybatis.guice.datasource.c3p0
    Contains c3p0 Data Source provider.
    org.mybatis.guice.datasource.dbcp
    Contains Apache commons-dbcp Data Source providers.
    org.mybatis.guice.datasource.druid
    Contains c3p0 Data Source provider.
    org.mybatis.guice.datasource.helper
    Contains helper classes to build and bind JDBC.driver and JDBC.url properties.
    org.mybatis.guice.datasource.hikaricp
    Contains core classes to build the HikariCP DataSource implementations through google-guice.
    org.mybatis.guice.environment
    Contains core classes to build the myBatis Environment through google-guice.
    org.mybatis.guice.mappers
    Contains the Provider and utility class to auto-bind requested mappers in the Google Guice binder.
    org.mybatis.guice.provision  
    org.mybatis.guice.session
    Defines Google Guice's providers for SqlSessionFactory and SqlSessionManager.
    org.mybatis.guice.transactional
    Contains classes to mark and handle transactional methods.
    org.mybatis.guice.type
